<question type="multichoice">
  <name>
    <text>Array and Matrix Transformation</text>
  </name>
  <questiontext format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[
Consider the following two methods in the same class.<br /><br />

public static void changeArray(int[] arr)<br />
{<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; for (int i = 0; i &lt; arr.length - 1; i++)<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; {<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; arr[i] = arr[i + 1];<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; }<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; arr[arr.length - 1] = arr[0];<br />
}<br /><br />

public static void changeMatrix(int[][] mat)<br />
{<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; for (int i = 0; i &lt; mat.length; i++)<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; {<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; changeArray(mat[i]);<br />
&#160;&#160;&#160; }<br />
}<br /><br />

If the current state of mat is:<br /><br />

1 2 3 4<br />
5 6 7 8<br /><br />

Which matrix will result from the method call changeMatrix(mat)?<br />
]]></text>
